Hi Maria Del Prete You recently made a Personal Motor claim and we'd like t=
o
hear about your experience.

As a forward thinking insurer, we're always looking for ways to do things
better.

Our survey should only take a couple of minutes and we sincerely thank you
for your time. Overall, how satisfied are you with your recent claims
experience? Very dissatisfied
<https://towerinsurance.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_2f8yoJdtiPwYO7c?Q_DL=3Dhu=
